      "content": "i found this old heavy signet ring in my grandmothers attic. it has this weird crest on it—a falcon perched on a broken sun. i've never seen anything like it in any history books and it doesn't look like any of the standard family crests. can u help me figure out what it might represent? it feels way too important to just be junk.",
