      "content": "the falcon/broken sun thing is a bit more than just \"symbolism\" to me. i found some old letters in the same box that mention a \"Kingdom of Aethelgard\" and how the royal line had to go into hiding to protect the bloodline. i thought it was just a story my family told, but seeing this ring... it makes so much sense. it's like there's a whole history they kept from us. do you think it's possible that a small kingdom actually existed but was just wiped from the official records?",
